sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant AC as AuthController
    participant U as User Model

    B->>AC: POST /login (name, pw)
    AC->>U: fetchByName(name)
    U-->>AC: player or null
    Note over AC: password_verify()
    Note over AC: Redirects to /login on invalid credentials
    Note over AC: Store player in session
    AC-->>B: Redirect /